你的邏輯其實是在驗證：

BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT 最終寫入的 HIGHRISK

= 同一個 TS_CUST_ID 底下所有 SK 帳號所對應的最高風險等級

你的案例：

TS_CUST_ID	SK_CUST_ID	HIGHRISK
A2730571670	A273057167	M
A2730571670	A273057167C	L
A2730571670	A273057167D	L

最高等級是 M

而最終：

select HIGHRISK
from BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT
where CustomerNo='A2730571670'

結果：

M

符合邏輯。

⸻

驗證全部客戶最簡單方式

先把風險等級轉成數字：

H = 3
M = 2
L = 1

然後找出每個 TS_CUST_ID 對應 SK 客戶中的最高等級。

⸻

Step1 找出來源應有的最高等級

WITH SRC AS
(
    SELECT
        s.TS_CUST_ID,
        MAX(
            CASE n.HIGHRISK
                WHEN 'H' THEN 3
                WHEN 'M' THEN 2
                WHEN 'L' THEN 1
            END
        ) AS SRC_RISK
    FROM BANCS_SK_CUST_INFO s
    JOIN Customer_Migrate_buffer c
        ON s.SK_CUST_ID = c.CustomerNo
    JOIN Cust_NP_Migrate_buffer n
        ON c.CIF_KEY = n.CIF_KEY
    GROUP BY s.TS_CUST_ID
)
SELECT *
FROM SRC;

⸻

Step2 取出 BSA 寫入結果

WITH TGT AS
(
    SELECT
        CustomerNo,
        CASE HIGHRISK
            WHEN 'H' THEN 3
            WHEN 'M' THEN 2
            WHEN 'L' THEN 1
        END AS TGT_RISK
    FROM BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT
)
SELECT *
FROM TGT;

⸻

Step3 比對差異

WITH SRC AS
(
    SELECT
        s.TS_CUST_ID,
        MAX(
            CASE n.HIGHRISK
                WHEN 'H' THEN 3
                WHEN 'M' THEN 2
                WHEN 'L' THEN 1
            END
        ) AS SRC_RISK
    FROM BANCS_SK_CUST_INFO s
    JOIN Customer_Migrate_buffer c
        ON s.SK_CUST_ID = c.CustomerNo
    JOIN Cust_NP_Migrate_buffer n
        ON c.CIF_KEY = n.CIF_KEY
    GROUP BY s.TS_CUST_ID
),
TGT AS
(
    SELECT
        CustomerNo,
        CASE HIGHRISK
            WHEN 'H' THEN 3
            WHEN 'M' THEN 2
            WHEN 'L' THEN 1
        END AS TGT_RISK
    FROM BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT
)
SELECT
    s.TS_CUST_ID,
    s.SRC_RISK,
    t.TGT_RISK
FROM SRC s
JOIN TGT t
    ON s.TS_CUST_ID = t.CustomerNo
WHERE s.SRC_RISK <> t.TGT_RISK;

