如果結果 = 0 筆

再驗證數量：

WITH SRC AS
(
    SELECT
        s.TS_CUST_ID,
        MAX(
            CASE n.HIGHRISK
                WHEN 'H' THEN 3
                WHEN 'M' THEN 2
                WHEN 'L' THEN 1
            END
        ) AS SRC_RISK
    FROM BANCS_SK_CUST_INFO s
    JOIN Customer_Migrate_buffer c
        ON s.SK_CUST_ID = c.CustomerNo
    JOIN Cust_NP_Migrate_buffer n
        ON c.CIF_KEY = n.CIF_KEY
    GROUP BY s.TS_CUST_ID
)
SELECT COUNT(*) AS SRC_CNT
FROM SRC;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS TGT_CNT
FROM BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT;

再跑：

-- 差異筆數
SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM
(
    WITH SRC AS (...)
    ,TGT AS (...)
    SELECT s.TS_CUST_ID
    FROM SRC s
    JOIN TGT t
        ON s.TS_CUST_ID=t.CustomerNo
    WHERE s.SRC_RISK<>t.TGT_RISK
) X;

驗證標準：

SRC_CNT = TGT_CNT
差異筆數 = 0

就能證明：

✓ 所有共有戶都取最高風險等級
✓ 沒有任何客戶被降級
✓ BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT 寫入結果完全符合規格

其實對 AML 驗證來說，這種「來源最大風險等級 vs 寫入結果」的差異筆數 = 0，就是最乾淨、最好交付給 QA 或客戶的驗證方式。